OL,3,CRoad closed after four-vehicle
OL,4,Ccollision involving coach
OL,6,FOne of Jersey's main roads is closed
OL,7,Fafter a major four-vehicle collision.
OL,9,FThe incident happened on Wednesday
OL,10,Fafternoon (1 July) on the Esplanade in
OL,11,FSt Helier, at the junction with
OL,12,FGloucester Street.
OL,14,FA 31-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of dangerous driving.
OL,17,FPeople are being asked to avoid the
OL,18,Farea and there is heavy traffic
OL,19,Fcongestion - with all three emergency
OL,20,Fservices in attendance.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/2
