OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1782917279
OL,3,CRoad closed after four-vehicle
OL,4,Ccollision involving coach
OL,6,FThe road is expected to be closed for
OL,7,Fsome time, with access blocked from La
OL,8,FRoute de la Liberation roundabout and
OL,9,Fthe underpass on to the Esplanade
OL,10,Fwestbound.
OL,12,FThe injuries are believed to be minor,
OL,13,Fwith one driver taken to the nearby
OL,14,FGeneral Hospital as a precaution.
